Mission Orders

Eliminate the enemies in the Gallery of Deceit and the Gallery of Lust of Azarel's Labyrinth and bring proof of their deaths.

Operation Target: {@LinkCreature:9#600#undying fighters}, {@LinkCreature:9#430#gula gutslashers}, {@LinkCreature:9#700#Alizarin imp hunters}, {@LinkCreature:9#710#Alizarin imp warders}, {@LinkCreature:9#800#gula butchers}, and {@LinkCreature:9#900#caiman cooks}.
It's a reward from the federation. Blessings to all the members of the Guild!
